# Diagnosis Data Contract

Source of truth: `src/types/diagnosis.ts`.

```ts
PersonalityCategory = 'empathy' | 'logic' | 'creativity' | 'leadership'
DiagnosticOption: { id, text, scores: Record<PersonalityCategory, number> }
DiagnosticQuestion: { id, index, text, category, options }
DiagnosisResult: { id, title, subtitle, baseAnalysis, themeColor, dominantCategory }
AIPromptBlueprint: { systemContext, temperature, maxTokens, responseSchema }
```

Rules:
- All option `scores` must include every `PersonalityCategory` key.
- Copywriting in Japanese (です・ます). Adult-cute, zero taboo (no alcohol, lucky numbers, religion).
- Result catalog lives in `lib/diagnosis/resultCatalog.ts` — do not hardcode titles in UI.
- Parse AI advice with Zod (`personalizedAdviceSchema`); always ship typed fallbacks.
